         <xocs:funding-text>The authors would like to thank the landowner partners for their support during sampling. To the SEDUC-MT and SME-Confresa for financial support during the first author's doctoral studies. FE supported by the Serrapilheira Institute fellowship/FAPESPA (grant number \u2013 R-2401\u201346863). TRF was supported by a grant from the UK Natural Environment Research Council (NERC) and S\u00E3o Paulo Research Foundation, Brazil (FAPESP) (NE/N011570/1, NE/W001691/1). BHMJR and BSM receive support from productivity fellowships PQ1 from the Brazilian National Council for Scientific and Technological Development (CNPq #311027/2019\u20139 and #303492/2022\u20138), as well as from the CNPq-PELD research project (#441572/2020\u20130) and the Mato Grosso State Research Support Foundation (FAPEMAT - #0346321/2020). We also appreciate the valuable contributions of the two anonymous reviewers to the final manuscript. During the preparation of this work, the authors used ChatGPT to check and improve the language of the manuscript. After using this tool, the authors reviewed and edited the content as needed and take full responsibility for the final content of the published article.</xocs:funding-text>
         <xocs:funding-text>The authors would like to thank the landowner partners for their support during sampling. To the SEDUC-MT and SME-Confresa for financial support during the first author's doctoral studies. FE supported by the Serrapilheira Institute fellowship/FAPESPA (grant number \u2013 R-2401-46863). TRF was supported by a grant from the UK Natural Environment Research Council (NERC) and S\u00E3o Paulo Research Foundation, Brazil (FAPESP) (NE/N011570/1, NE/W001691/1). BHMJR and BSM receive support from productivity fellowships PQ1 from the Brazilian National Council for Scientific and Technological Development (CNPq #311027/2019-9 and #303492/2022-8), as well as from the CNPq-PELD research project (#441572/2020-0) and the Mato Grosso State Research Support Foundation (FAPEMAT - #0346321/2020). We also appreciate the valuable contributions of the two anonymous reviewers to the final manuscript. </xocs:funding-text>
